posts.name: Sam Carlberg
posts.cooked: Your code seems to be instantiating the drive subsystem multiple times, which would cause this error. Subsystems should be instantiated once, in the RobotContainer class. They can be passed to other object constructors or method calls as needed
Thank you this worked I changed the other files that had subystems in it to take parameters of the needed subystem.
